WEBVTT

00:01.240 --> 00:05.028
<i>Last time on Married with Children,
there was a death in the family.</i>

00:05.240 --> 00:06.992
Clear!

00:10.440 --> 00:14.069
It's exactly what I feared, Mr. Bundy.
The fuel pump.

00:15.560 --> 00:17.437
Now, unfortunately,
finding a donor pump...

00:17.640 --> 00:19.949
...will be nearly impossible.

00:20.160 --> 00:23.914
There's a rumour that
the fuel pump you need is in Cuba.

00:24.880 --> 00:26.996
Cuba.

00:27.200 --> 00:30.397
Sultry, seductive Cuba.

00:30.640 --> 00:31.834
Unbelievable.

00:32.080 --> 00:36.278
A collector in DÃ¼sseldorf will give us
5 grand for the entire engine.

00:37.280 --> 00:40.795
Oh, no, don't leave me alone.

00:41.320 --> 00:44.073
Drive towards the light, old friend.

00:45.440 --> 00:47.715
Drive towards the light.

00:49.000 --> 00:55.074
